Here's my solution to the Windows 7 constant crashing problem... the same thing was happening to me on my brand new laptop which I bought just for DJing parties. You can imagine how disappointed I was...
1- Update your sound card driver.
Additionally to avoid crashes, TURN YOUR WIFI OFF! Traktor forums list this as the number one cause for crashes. Once I did this, everything was smooth sailing.
